\newlabel{fig:enron_deg}{{3}{5}{Degree distribution of the Enron email network (undirected projection, log scale). The distribution is heavy-tailed, with a small number of addresses — primarily executive inboxes and distribution lists — receiving a disproportionate volume of mail}{figure.caption.4}{}}
